 style="width:100%;height:90px;display:block;background:#111;border-radius:8px"></canvas><div class="legend"><span class="cyan"><i class="sq" style="background:#64d2ff"></i>예상</span><span class="green"><i class="sq" style="background:#30d158"></i>실제</span></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-hdr"><div class="card-title">현재시간 예상 VS 실제 발전량</div><div class="card-sub">현재 1시간 기준</div></div><div class="mini-grid"><div class="mini"><div class="mini-l">예상 발전량</div><div class="mini-v cyan" id="cur-pred">0.00 Wh</div></div><div class="mini"><div class="mini-l">실제 발전량</div><div class="mini-v green" id="cur-actual">0.00 Wh</div></div></div><div style="margin-top:8px"><div class="mini"><div class="mini-l">오차율</div><div class="mini-v" id="cur-error">0.00%</div></div></div></div><div class="page-dots"><div class="page-dot"></div><div class="page-dot active"></div><div class="page-dot"></div></div></div>
