 id="ch1i">--</td><td class="green" id="ch1p">--</td></tr><tr><td>CH3 Load</td><td id="ch2v">--</td><td id="ch2i">--</td><td class="cyan" id="ch2p">--</td></tr></table></div><div class="card"><div class="card-hdr"><div class="card-title">배터리 쿨롱 카운팅</div><div class="card-sub">BMS 상세</div></div><div class="mini-grid"><div class="mini"><div class="mini-l">잔량</div><div class="mini-v green" id="bms-ah">-- Ah</div><div class="sub" id="bms-cap">/ -- Ah</div></div><div class="mini"><div class="mini-l">SOC</div><div class="mini-v green" id="bms-soc">--%</div><div class="sub" id="bms-eco">ECO 기준 --%</div></div></div><div style="margin-top:8px"><div class="prog-row"><div class="pr-lbl">SOC</div><div class="pr-bar"><div class="pr-fill" id="soc-bar" style="width:0;background:#30d158"></div></div><div class="pr-val" id="soc-val">--%</div></div><div class="prog-row"><div class="pr-lbl">OCV</div><div class="pr-bar"><div class="pr-fill" id="ocv-bar" style="width:0;background:#64d2ff"></div></div><div class="pr-val" id="ocv-val">--V</div></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-hdr"><div class="card-title">이벤트 로그</div><div class="card-sub">최근 상태</div></div><div id="log-list"></div></div><div class="page-dots"><div class="page-dot"></div><div class="page-dot"></div><div class="page-dot active"></div></div></div>
